STATE of North Carolina
v.
Dewayne PARKER No. 393P08-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. May 17, 2017 Dwayne Parker, for Parker. Amy C. Kunstling, Roger A. Echols, District Attorney, for the State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 17th of May 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Durham County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of May 2017."
